dc:description: Brownish yellow glass. Broken and partially mended. Material fair. Black impurities especially inside rim. Some bubbles. Blowing spirals with traces of stone. A rough area which may be devitrification on part of neck and extending onto shoulder. Rim outsplayed from neck and folded upward and inward. Cylindrical neck with horizontal constriction at its base. Marks of tool which made constriction at its base. Inverted piriform body. Base with kick.
